data.description: Impeccably designed and meticulously maintained, this sought-after Myers Park townhome offers a rare opportunity to experience a more maintenance free lifestyle in the desirable and unincorporated Johns Creek location.. Boasting an expansive floor plan spread across three levels, main floor hardwoods, new paint, loads of storage and so much more, this residence exudes sophistication and functionality at every turn. The main level features a master suite, while an additional master suite awaits upstairs, alongside two generously proportioned bedrooms. With multiple living areas, including a family room adorned with built-ins and a gas fireplace, as well as a versatile bonus space perfect for various lifestyle needs, this home effortlessly accommodates modern living.  The gourmet kitchen is flooded with light and impresses with its large granite breakfast bar and two-story breakfast room? A haven for culinary enthusiasts. Entertain with ease in the formal dining room or retreat to the fenced private backyard, newly updated with gorgeous plantings, sod and a patio, for al fresco gatherings. You'll also enjoy access to community amenities such as a pool, clubhouse, and fitness center. The best Johns Creek schools and convenient access to interstates, shopping and more! Experience the pinnacle of comfort and convenience in this distinguished abode today!
